    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nHave a run here that could become a lucrative regular thing if we can pull it off.  This\u2019ll take you into Pyro, so you\u2019ll have to be ready to tangle with some of the locals. \n\nYou\u2019ll need to grab the stuff from <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>, make the jump to Pyro, and then get to <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>. \n\nAll you need to do is bring a ship with space for <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4>, a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4>, and be ready to do some damage if someone picks a fight with you.",
